WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:00.960
Elder brother

00:01.360 --> 00:02.600
Even if I were utterly reckless

00:03.400 --> 00:04.200
I would never do such

00:04.200 --> 00:05.360
Treasonous things

00:07.000 --> 00:08.040
Those noble families

00:08.240 --> 00:10.360
Want our Sikong family to fight among ourselves

00:10.880 --> 00:12.360
So they can profit from it

00:13.400 --> 00:14.520
The people are saying

00:15.120 --> 00:17.200
Chen and Sikong share the realm

00:18.240 --> 00:18.760
These words

00:18.760 --> 00:20.160
Can you bear to hear?

00:22.960 --> 00:23.840
Elder brother

00:25.920 --> 00:26.480
Elder brother

00:27.600 --> 00:28.440
Do you really want

00:28.640 --> 00:29.840
Brothers to harm each other?

00:35.960 --> 00:37.400
Since you won't confess

00:38.360 --> 00:39.920
Then suffer some physical pain

00:40.280 --> 00:40.960
Beat him

00:41.440 --> 00:42.000
Yes
